Acheron Flurry	CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:General	VISIBLE:YES				PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Improved Unarmed Strike						PRESKILL:1,Knowledge (The Planes)=4			PRESTAT:2,DEX=15,WIS=15									DESC:During your turn, designate an opponent within reach to whom you have dealt damage during this encounter using an unarmed strike. You can spend a standard action to confound and distract your chosen foe with a constant flood of distracting mock attacks. While doing this leaves you open to attacks (applying a -2 penalty to your Armor Class), your foe may take only a single standard action or move action on his next turn. If you move away (or are otherwise no longer conscious and adjacent to your foe) before your chosen foe's next turn, he may act normally.									TEMPBONUS:PC|COMBAT|AC|-2								SOURCEPAGE:PH			
Air Heritage	CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:Heritage	VISIBLE:YES																						DESC:Your fly speed increases by 30 feet (up to a maximum increase equal to your normal fly speed). If you don't have a fly speed as a racial ability, this benefit has no effect. You also gain a +2 bonus on Balance and Jump checks when carrying a light load or no load and wearing light armor or no armor.													BONUS:SKILL|Balance,Jump|2|PREVARLT:ENCUMBERANCE,1,var("COUNT[EQTYPE.ARMOR.IS.HEAVY]"),1,var("COUNT[EQTYPE.ARMOR.IS.MEDIUM]"),1				SOURCEPAGE:PH	BONUS:MOVEADD|TYPE.Walk|30|PREMOVE:1,Fly=1		
