Celestial Summoning Specialist	CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:General	VISIBLE:YES							PREALIGN:LG,LN,NG,TN,CG,CN			PRESKILL:2,Knowledge (The Planes)=2,Knowledge (Religion)=2								PRESPELL:1,Summon Monster I,Summon Monster II,Summon Monster III,Summon Monster IV,Summon Monster V,Summon Monster VISummon Monster VII,Summon Monster VIII,Summon Monster IX				DESC:Add one good-aligned creature to the list of creatures for each summon monster spell that you can cast. (Work with the DM to select creatures appropriate to the spell's list of summonable creatures.) Each time you gain the ability to cast a new summon monster spell, you may add one good-aligned creature to the list.																	SOURCEPAGE:PH			
